IjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9JbnN0YW50LVBvdC02UXQtUGx1cy1XaUZpL2RwL0IwOFRNVEpaOEw_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAb7dOQ1T8HiMZqmwGk25Sn9vOunqIxlNZOxS2KjXkU79&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FInstant-Pot-6Qt-Plus-WiFi%2Fdp%2FB08TMTJZ8L&amp;uuid=cn2c6ndkenMEwdUI20429">Instant Pot Pro Plus</a> 。它不仅具有罐装功能和烤箱安全内锅等更新功能，而且您还可以获得 WiFi 连接和配套应用程序，该应用程序提供 800 多种食谱的分步指导说明。另外，您可以使用它远程释放 Instant Pot 的蒸汽。您还可以使用该应用程序设置定时器以自动释放蒸汽。</p><h2>最佳温度计：Thermapen One</h2><p><core-commerce id="943252bcac88489babe3a0cd4a07486a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>没有人愿意吃未煮熟的肉，但如果煮得太熟也很难吃。避免极端情况的一种方法是使用温度计来监测温度。我们最喜欢的是 ThermoWorks 的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8ec42127-5c25-4160-a755-9edb36e27b1b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=ThermoWorks&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4ZWM0MjEyNy01YzI1LTQxNjAtYTc1NS05ZWRiMzZlMjdiMWIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlcm1vd29ya3MuY29tL3RoZXJtYXBlbi1vbmUvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NDI2Y2Y2ZS1mOTM0LTQ2MTktODk3Yy04MDA2OTI4ODY5NmMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAbZA6ZAQv7OdX3jRoiFue3rlL_y3vV2PZQpN7k7nJtDW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thermoworks.com%2Fthermapen-one%2F&amp;uuid=Wld7Y95NhItvgGa523430">Thermapen One</a> 。它会即时提供读数，并且屏幕会根据您的握持方式自动旋转。自动唤醒和睡眠功能有助于快速检查温度，其 IP67 防水等级意味着您不必担心不小心将其掉入水槽。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8ec42127-5c25-4160-a755-9edb36e27b1b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=ThermoWorks&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4ZWM0MjEyNy01YzI1LTQxNjAtYTc1NS05ZWRiMzZlMjdiMWIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhlcm1vd29ya3MuY29tL3RoZXJtb3BvcC8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcs0itC1JHopjRhRR6lSzrJrrueVgce6J15Ua-KfdlXN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thermoworks.com%2Fthermopop%2F&amp;uuid=YvoYRg1dBJ9c65f024430">ThermoPop</a>是 ThermoWorks 产品线中更实惠的选择。它不如 Thermapen One 快，并且没有旋转显示屏或背光。但它仍能准确测量温度，虽然不防水，但防溅。</p><h2>最佳食物秤：Escali Primo</h2><p><core-commerce id="6da8038591c44b9795273fe28f300478" data-type="product-list"></p><p>各地的面包师都知道，测量配料最精确的方法是使用秤。 “一杯面粉”可能会因舀取方式的不同而大相径庭，而秤可以准确告诉您是否有 120 克。数字秤最适合进行最准确的测量，我们尤其喜欢<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Fc2NhbGktUDExNUMtUHJlY2lzaW9uLUxpZ2h0d2VpZ2h0LUxpZmV0aW1lL2RwL0IwMDA3R0FXUlM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAe-fPMkgjhmKwoQt0pLrmVGhTlGBRaAkXG0SUS9LzbrN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FEscali-P115C-Precision-Lightweight-Lifetime%2Fdp%2FB0007GAWRS&amp;uuid=TJdRmXVhxSnAFJeA27430">Escali Primo</a> 。您只需按一下就可以在克和盎司之间切换，重要的是，还有一个去皮按钮可以将重量归零，这样您就可以在同一个容器中继续测量。与其他型号相比，我们喜欢 Escali Primo 的原因之一是它有一个非常长的自动关闭定时器，允许它在关闭前保持开启四分钟。当您需要额外的时间来切碎蔬菜或收集其他成分时，这很重要，而不必担心秤会重置为零。</p><h2>最佳空气炸锅：Instant Vortex Plus</h2><p><core-commerce id="0f0335dff28543b9aa5dfc84dd216784" data-type="product-list"></p><p>现在最热门的厨房用具似乎是<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-air-fryers-133047180.html">空气炸锅</a>，大概是因为“油炸”食物而没有油腻的想法很容易推销。不过，实际上，空气炸锅只是微型对流烤箱。它们通常是豆荚形的，通常带有一个可拆卸的篮子。如果您更喜欢在工作台面上放置多功能设备，还有带空气煎炸功能的电烤箱 - 请参阅下面的建议。</p><p>虽然两者各有千秋，但如果你觉得自己会经常气炸，其实我们推荐一款专用的豆荚形空气炸锅。这些设备往往会产生更脆的食物，而且它们更容易清洁。我们最喜欢的产品之一是带有 ClearCook 和 OdorErase 的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb4JdazcvxYKKhSxpmxqT2xXhdSUUaFWfr2y5NkmHPjo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FVortexTM-Fryer-ClearCook-OdorErase-Stainless%2Fdp%2FB096N28SZP&amp;uuid=3gu68l3dTakVrFeX31431">Instant Vortex Plus</a> 。顾名思义，它有一个窗口，您可以看到正在烹饪的东西，还有有助于减少烹饪气味的除味过滤器——没有多少其他空气炸锅同时具备这两种功能。它也不会像大型烤箱那样占用太多空间，并且具有易于使用的控件。</p><h2>最佳立式搅拌机：KitchenAid Artisan 系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="81dcd6f2cad94818943e93db4b1dd799" data-type="product-list"></p><p>当然，您可以用手将一批曲奇面团混合在一起，但这需要时间和相当多的上半身力量。如果您想揉面团或搅打蛋白酥皮，那就更是如此了。买立式搅拌机省去麻烦。多年来，面包师和业余厨师最喜欢的是<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3cce5c02-7bee-4131-8179-faba77391773&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=KitchenAid&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUtjh2ODLXKbzH9R4JLONL-ghvSNeTMeQXYI3NPj58YR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kitchenaid.com%2Fcountertop-appliances%2Fstand-mixers%2Ftilt-head-stand-mixers%2Fp.artisan-series-5-quart-tilt-head-stand-mixer.ksm150psaq.html%3F&amp;uuid=jvEPDuVvvjESUJqN34432">KitchenAid 的 Artisan 系列</a>。它经久耐用，功能强大，并配有您选择的桨、钩和搅拌器附件，可与搅拌碗一起使用。我们还喜欢 KitchenAid 搅拌机与各种配件和附件兼容，这些配件和附件可以将机器变成<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbjLUAUzsTNu_gapUmn-ihSKaMV3Av27PKJ4qshSh-Q7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKitchenAid-KAICA-Cream-Maker-Attachment%2Fdp%2FB00O4XR5QQ&amp;uuid=Tr6ItQzzF9MIUlNB35432">冰淇淋机</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9LaXRjaGVuQWlkLUtTTU1HQS1HcmluZGVyLUF0dGFjaG1lbnQtU2lsdmVyL2RwL0IwN0dLN1hLSks_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUwgFQV99zES8z9xDLYx0WTuLXBc-b3S8NI86SD8z9Pg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKitchenAid-KSMMGA-Grinder-Attachment-Silver%2Fdp%2FB07GK7XKJK&amp;uuid=0wE3yyoGiyQ21mXk36432">绞肉机</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9LaXRjaGVuQWlkLUtTTVBSQS0zLVBpZWNlLVJvbGxlci1BdHRhY2htZW50L2RwL0IwMURCR1FSMUs_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWzG_ZvySsWJ9T7FW-kF8CaeKVbhvoeXD-gjom-OuTlp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FKitchenAid-KSMPRA-3-Piece-Roller-Attachment%2Fdp%2FB01DBGQR1K&amp;uuid=93HZeQGAMTlTLMNj37432">意大利面机</a>，以防您想扩大您的烹饪视野。</p><h2>最佳搅拌机：Vitamix Explorian 系列</h2><p><core-commerce id="9acd69437b2645d2b0aab3a339d9fd61" data-type="product-list"></p><p>在这个领域很难击败<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODQyNmNmNmUtZjkzNC00NjE5LTg5N2MtODAwNjkyODg2OTZjIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAXw5g_9UmSODbAVtQAZtkA6uAfMjrG2X7njQQY8HnwlY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2F%3F&amp;uuid=2CTm15DSUdoHasOS40433">Vitamix</a> 。这个高性能搅拌机品牌生产的机器不仅可以制作冰沙，还可以制作沙拉酱、酱汁、面糊和汤。如果您习惯于在食谱中添加更坚韧的成分（例如坚果、干果和冷冻农产品），它会特别方便。其他功率较弱的搅拌机可能会在您加入较坚硬的原料后留下大块，而 Vitamix 不会，为您留下丝般柔滑的最终产品。</p><p>根据您获得的型号，您还可以购买不同的附件以充分利用搅拌机的强大底座。您可以拿起<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvc2hvcC9sb3ctcHJvZmlsZS02NC1vdW5jZS1jb250YWluZXI_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NDI2Y2Y2ZS1mOTM0LTQ2MTktODk3Yy04MDA2OTI4ODY5NmMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAY56y00hCt4I-uR25QkyoV8SCwWjigxX1ocYkJ0oohzX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2Flow-profile-64-ounce-container%3F&amp;uuid=CPlu3P37W6x0QLUD41433">64 盎司的容器</a>一次为全家人制作冰沙，或者拿起一个<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASzygJrxMFyNUR0zy5LBr973hSM5gTubnn6RFWajyiwa&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2F48-ounce-dry-grains-container-with-self-detect%3F&amp;uuid=fFLCu00Qwi09mYxL42433">“干谷物”容器</a>，该容器配备专门用于研磨全谷物等东西的刀片，这样您就可以制作自己的面粉。</p><p> Vitamix 目前有四个系列的搅拌机：基本款<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvc2hvcC92aXRhbWl4LW9uZSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODQyNmNmNmUtZjkzNC00NjE5LTg5N2MtODAwNjkyODg2OTZjIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAVWZAMzpll2m2ukRVSY0uOPcbVsBLLPPR-Hm1FFv9sLe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2Fvitamix-one&amp;uuid=VDGTdX3QNbCUjmej43434">Vitamix One</a> ，售价 250 美元；稍微高级一点的<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvc2hvcC9lMzEwPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODQyNmNmNmUtZjkzNC00NjE5LTg5N2MtODAwNjkyODg2OTZjIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAT-w5-6YiABfCb4LvnxE56EoXzfLOSnCivbAd0FtVwsP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2Fe310%3F&amp;uuid=dWvFWZFiubOYp2ig44434">Explorian 系列</a>，起价 350 美元，可以说是最适合大多数人的产品； <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvc2hvcC9jbGFzc2ljLWJsZW5kZXJzPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODQyNmNmNmUtZjkzNC00NjE5LTg5N2MtODAwNjkyODg2OTZjIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfD3GqguLLG1cO9H06_X1uwz0pHQR8kT-499585_7Bfe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2Fclassic-blenders%3F&amp;uuid=zVrLtwn7gcqbjTIS45434">Legacy 系列</a>，起价 400 美元；和高级<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4052d411-fe73-431e-851f-5cfdc282e4c1&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Vitamix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0MDUyZDQxMS1mZTczLTQzMWUtODUxZi01Y2ZkYzI4MmU0YzEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudml0YW1peC5jb20vdXMvZW5fdXMvc2hvcC9zbWFydC1zeXN0ZW0tYmxlbmRlcnM_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NDI2Y2Y2ZS1mOTM0LTQ2MTktODk3Yy04MDA2OTI4ODY5NmMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAR8U8DxOLHs92QNMrD9yPQbuMmFgowNrCnDcNm_W-IFq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vitamix.com%2Fus%2Fen_us%2Fshop%2Fsmart-system-blenders%3F&amp;uuid=A0GoYXPHQjTOQH3q46434">Ascent 系列</a>，至少要花费 500 美元。是的，这些都是昂贵的机器，但如果您进行大量混合或喜欢尝试从头开始制作东西，则值得投资。</p><h2>最佳电烤箱：Breville Smart Oven Air Fryer Pro</h2><p><core-commerce id="63662e9b9cf3462e96e9a27c4925d514" data-type="product-list"></p><p>电烤箱是一种用途广泛的电器。是的，您可以用它来烤面包、面包和各种烘焙食品。但如果您不想用全尺寸烤箱加热整个房子，它也是一个很好的选择。它的加热速度也快得多，这使其成为加热剩菜的更有效选择。</p><p>我们喜欢<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX7fEkqdXpqvpmw0oO5FsdhZuGqd2WelxyqAA1BBAOOa&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBreville-BOV900BSS-Convection-Brushed-Stainless%2Fdp%2FB01N5UPTZS%2F&amp;uuid=IGVmFMrUFbnmkmJJ50435">Breville Smart Oven Air Fryer Pro</a> ，因为它大到足以烤一只鸡，而且它还具有其他功能，如脱水、发酵和空气炸（得益于超级对流模式）。它还包括用于烘烤比萨饼和烘烤百吉饼的预设。 <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=c0ca87c7-692e-4b52-8410-9ea74ef1a5a6&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Breville&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeJViXdMtCLqcuxxGdLYFQFv1U9qLHNZVwn4yhKLSevS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breville.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fovens%2Fbov950.html%3Fsku%3DBOV950BSS1BUS1%26&amp;uuid=0L6uUZUR1U8yekLE51435">Joule Oven Air Fryer Pro</a>是 Joule Oven Air Fryer Pro 的升级版，它增加了 WiFi 连接，因此您可以通过手机控制它。该应用程序也有很多食谱，还有一个“自动驾驶仪”功能，可以在烹饪过程中自动调节温度。</p><p>如果您不想要这么大的东西，一个更小、更实惠的选择是<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9QYW5hc29uaWMtTkItRzExMFAtRmxhc2hYcHJlc3MtSW5mcmFyZWQtUmVtb3ZhYmxlL2RwL0IwMDhDOVVGREk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAATU_N_q2EJZhdFpL_m8w05s0eFcEiTxSBJdVFV4guJP8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPanasonic-NB-G110P-FlashXpress-Infrared-Removable%2Fdp%2FB008C9UFDI%3F&amp;uuid=exPD8o7OUO8uqaoy52435">Panasonic Flash Express</a> 。它的空间足以容纳一片披萨，但绝对不会像 Breville 那样占用太多空间。如果您想要的只是一个用于加热冷冻零食或一次烤几片面包的烤箱，这绝对是一个不错的选择。</p><h2>最佳真空低温烹调机：Anova Precision Cooker 3.0</h2><p><core-commerce id="b61b6925c56045e1861a59e5df4c2a2a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果你想确保你的昂贵牛排是半熟的而不需要经常监控它的温度，可以考虑买一个真空低温烹调法。这些机器让您可以在温控水浴中烹饪任何东西，从而做到完美。我们已经用真空低温烹调法<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-12-19-sous-vide-guide.html">成功地制作了</a>牛排、鸡肉、汉堡、鸡蛋甚至酸奶，而且每次的结果都很完美。</p><p>我们最喜欢的型号是<a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Bbm92YS1DdWxpbmFyeS1BTjUyNS1VUzAwLVByZWNpc2lvbi1Db29rZXIvZHAvQjBCUTlGNTZXVi8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tczMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg0MjZjZjZlLWY5MzQtNDYxOS04OTdjLTgwMDY5Mjg4Njk2YyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAakr9X5LnpKR2_kUBQNmXMlUtnZA-pqdd5dFWWHhZlAG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAnova-Culinary-AN525-US00-Precision-Cooker%2Fdp%2FB0BQ9F56WV%2F&amp;uuid=Ya9u4g74gEHMxpEY56436">Anova Precision Cooker 3.0</a> 。随着最新版本的推出，该公司为已经非常出色的基础产品增加了数字触摸控制、更长的电源线和 WiFi 连接。配套应用程序也经过精心设计，具有数百种食谱和远程控制机器的选项。即使有一个应用程序组件，您也不必使用它；您可以使用机载控件和大型数字显示屏轻松调节温度。</p><p> <em>Valentina Palladino 为本报告做出了贡献。</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https:/